													"value": "[Yurgir] an orthon aims a crossbow at the player (aimed from the hip) <Greg>"
												}
											},
											{
												"key": {
													"type": 22,
													"value": "Attitude"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "Default"
												}
											},
											{
												"key": {
													"type": 22,
													"value": "CinematicNodeContext"
												},
												"val": {
													"type": 23,
													"value": "The player enters a gore-soaked alcove and approaches the displacer.There's various severed heads on display - people and monsters. A pile of eviscerated corpses forms a throne-chaise.\r\nThere's suddenly a loud click from above (implied to be the orthon racking/loading its crossbow). The player looks up.\r\nThe orthon looms on a gallery/crumpling floor overlooking the alcove. It aims a crossbow at the player. Flanking it are several merregons."
												}
											},
											{
												"key": {
													"type": 22,
													"value": "CinematicObjects"
												},
