				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "Dialogue with the Orthon, where he tells you it was ordered by Raphael to kill Ketheric's Dark Justiciars. The dialogue ends in combat, unless you succeed some very hard persuasions.\r\nOrthon is huge, forboding and loves a good fight. He speaks in a low rumble and is TERRIFYING. "
				}
